item.title: CVE-2023-5957|2024-08-02T08:14:25.192Z -- unknown -- ni%20purchase%20order%28po%29%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Ni Purchase Order(PO) For WooCommerce WordPress plugin through 1.2.1 does not validate logo and signature image files uploaded in the settings, allowing high privileged user to upload arbitrary files to the web server, triggering an RCE vulnerability by uploading a web shell.
